<p><strong>Sources</strong> <Link to="/source/seekers_of_secrets">Seekers of Secrets pg. 48</Link><br/><strong>Price</strong> 16,000 gp<br/>This stone grants a +2 enhancement bonus to Constitution per stone, stacking up to +4 total. These stones do not stack with non-flawed onyx rhomboid ioun stones.</p>
